data.description: Brick ranch-style home, located in the Mona Shores School District, just down the road from Lake Harbor Park. This home features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms that could be easily converted back to a full 2, an updated kitchen, a wood-burning tiled fireplace, a full basement, and an attached garage. This home sits on a peaceful, deep, wooded-backyard with a large 20x14 storage shed. Call today for your private showing!  Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
